high_descs: Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the cabinet.
Pick up tissue box from the cabinet.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dresser on your right.
Place tissue on the dresser.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near bed.
Pick up tissue box from the cabinet.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dresser on your right.
Place tissue on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Obtaining tissue box from various locations and arranging them in a dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the cabinet.
Pick up tissue box from the cabinet.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dresser on your right.
Place tissue box on the dresser.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the bed.
Pick up tissue box from the cabinet.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dresser on your right.
Place tissue box on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Obtaining tissue box from various locations and arranging them in a dresser.

high_descs: Turn back and walk towards the cabinet.
Pick up the tissue box from the middle shelf down rack of the cabinet.
Turn back towards the dresser.
Put the tissue box on the top left corner of the dresser.
Turn back and come towards the cabinet, then turn right and walk, head to the bed.
Pick up the tissue box from the bed.
Come back towards the dresser.
Stand up the tissue box right side of the first tissue box on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put two tissue boxes on the dresser.
